This extension was developed to extract images from PDF documents, offering the capability to extract images from specific pages or all pages within a PDF file.

ЁЯЪА  Key Features:
тЬЕ Extract images from the entire PDF file or from specific pages.
тЬЕ Download all extracted images.
тЬЕ Download images individually.
